Preconditions:
**Example notification template:**
{% capture content %}

<div>Renders the content by captured keyword.</div>

<div>Can use template variables: <b>{{ customer_order.number }}</b></div>

<div><b>{{customer_order.cancel_reason}}</b></div>


**Example notification sample data:**
{
 "customerOrder": {
"number": "some number",
"cancelReason": "asd",
"number1": "some number"
}
}


**Example layout template:**

<div><b>HEADER</b></div>


{{ content }}

<div>FOOTER</div>
